WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.350
Hey, good morning family. I have a

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:05.749
great video here for you. I have a

00:00:05.759 --> 00:00:07.269
great testimony—something that I've

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:09.350
been believing God for, and the Lord came

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:11.830
through. I just came on today

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.150
to tell you about the goodness of God

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:17.430
and what faith can do. First

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:19.830
