00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:22.230
the likes, all the shares, and all

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.230
the kind words in the comment

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:27.429
section. God is so good. He told me to

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:29.109
start this channel back at the first of

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:31.669
the year, and to see what the Lord has

00:00:31.679 --> 00:00:34.069
done in such a short amount of time

00:00:34.069 --> 00:00:34.079
has

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:36.389
been amazing. I just want to

00:00:36.399 --> 00:00:37.910
say thank you from

00:00:37.920 --> 00:00:39.910
the bottom of my heart, for my wife's

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:41.670
