00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:43.270
say thank you for all the love gifts

00:00:43.270 --> 00:00:43.280
and

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:44.869
for all of the support that you're

00:00:44.879 --> 00:00:46.790
showing us. We just want to let you

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:48.470
know we pray for you. We're believing

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:50.950
for your miracles, for a

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.470
turnaround in your finances,

00:00:52.470 --> 00:00:52.480
and

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:54.389
for healing in your

00:00:54.399 --> 00:00:57.350
bodies. I just believe that

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:00.549
nothing is impossible to him who

00:01:00.549 --> 00:01:00.559
believes,

00:01:00.559 --> 00:01:03.590
and God is still doing miracles today.

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:05.670
Here's a miracle that God did for

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:08.149
me. At the beginning of this year, I

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:10.550
had the same mower. I have a little

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:13.270
over an acre of land that I take care

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:15.910
of every week in the

00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:17.190
summer and the spring, and

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:18.390
then through the fall. I have a lot

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.149
of trees, and the trees drop all the

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:22.149
leaves. I've had the same

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:25.190
mower now for going on 20 years.

00:01:28.479 --> 00:01:31.590
The transmission belt that makes

00:01:31.590 --> 00:01:31.600
it go

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:34.149
was slipping really bad.

00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:35.429
I started looking at how much

00:01:35.439 --> 00:01:37.510
mowers cost and pricing them.

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.830
For my land and how much of a mower I

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:41.910
needed, it was going to cost thousands

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:44.390
and thousands of dollars. I

00:01:44.390 --> 00:01:44.400
said,

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:46.149
'Lord, I don't

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:47.510
want to spend that kind of money on a

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:49.510
credit card or try to do this right now.

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:52.069
I'm just going to use this mower as

00:01:52.079 --> 00:01:53.990
much as I

00:01:53.990 --> 00:01:54.000
