00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.069
anointed it with oil, started praying

00:01:56.079 --> 00:01:58.630
over my mower, and I just had to drive

00:01:58.630 --> 00:01:58.640
really

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.870
slow.

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:03.109
Here we are in

00:02:03.119 --> 00:02:05.109
August, and all through the

00:02:05.119 --> 00:02:06.709
summer, it

00:02:06.709 --> 00:02:06.719
was

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:08.790
just driving really slow; it

00:02:08.790 --> 00:02:08.800
took

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:10.469
me forever to mow this

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:13.670
land. I didn't

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.510
complain; it was

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:16.949
irritating, but I just

00:02:16.949 --> 00:02:16.959
used

00:02:16.959 --> 00:02:18.309
it as prayer time.

00:02:18.309 --> 00:02:18.319
The

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:20.550
more time I had to mow, the more time I

00:02:20.550 --> 00:02:20.560
spent

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.710
praying in the spirit and

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:24.869
seeking Him. It

00:02:24.869 --> 00:02:24.879
was

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:26.550
just my private time

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:29.350
mowing grass. Lo and behold, I was

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:31.030
