00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:37.040
with

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:40.869
a mower on a trailer in the back.

00:02:40.879 --> 00:02:43.509
She jumped out

00:02:43.509 --> 00:02:43.519
of

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:46.710
the truck and said, 'Brandon,

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:49.830
the Lord spoke to me in my yard last

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:52.630
