00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:02.710
said it's brand new and has

00:03:02.720 --> 00:03:04.869
the bagger and everything. This

00:03:04.879 --> 00:03:06.790
mower is top of the line—the Cadillac of mowers. It's

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:08.949
one of the best

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:10.869
mowers you can buy on the market;

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:12.470
it doesn't get any better, really.

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:15.110
The engine

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:17.110
is really big. This

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:19.990
sucker's huge. She

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.790
and her husband got out and said, 'We

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:25.750
believe the Lord spoke to us

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:28.390
to give you this mower to use for your

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:29.910
