00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:32.390
said, 'Are you kidding me?'and they

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:34.229
said, 'Yeah.'She was crying and

00:03:34.239 --> 00:03:36.229
he was crying;

00:03:36.239 --> 00:03:37.830
it was a

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.990
sacrificial gift.

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:42.470
I was so taken aback by it. I just

00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:42.480
said,

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:44.550
'Praise God,'because I've been

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:47.270
believing for this mower and the Lord

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:49.830
came through. I'm

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:51.589
not bragging about what God did; I'm

00:03:51.589 --> 00:03:51.599
rejoicing

00:03:51.599 --> 00:03:53.350
in

00:03:53.350 --> 00:03:53.360
it.

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:55.830
I'm trying to tell you that faith can do

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:58.550
