00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:09.830
They rolled that mower down

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:12.630
off that trailer and said,

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:14.470
'Here you go.'They taught me how to use

00:04:14.470 --> 00:04:14.480
it—it

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:16.069
took a bit because

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:18.550
it had all these buttons and

00:04:18.550 --> 00:04:18.560
features.

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:20.629
It was just amazing.

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:22.469
As

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:25.030
I

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:27.430
said, it has the bagger for

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:29.590
the leaves for the coming fall.

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:31.510
Everything I ever wanted

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:34.310
in a mower, God gave it to me today. I

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:36.150
just want to tell you right now how good

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:39.030
God is. God is a good God, He loves

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:41.430
you so much, and He provided for me again

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:44.390
today with something that was

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:46.310
like the Cadillac of mowers. It's

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:48.870
not like a little push

00:04:48.880 --> 00:04:50.469
mower; He gave me the best

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:53.430
of the best of a rider and, in

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:54.790
the world scene, I'm just telling you

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:56.469
it doesn't get any better than that.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:02.629
If God can do it for me, He can do it

00:05:02.639 --> 00:05:05.590
for you. I didn't complain about it; I

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:08.070
tried to be thankful for what I had and

00:05:08.070 --> 00:05:08.080
keep

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.990
a good attitude, regardless

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.350
if that belt was slipping. I

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:13.110
anointed it with oil and kept praying

00:05:13.120 --> 00:05:15.670
over it, 'Little mower, you're

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:17.430
going to last all through the summer;

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:19.189
you're not going to fall

00:05:19.189 --> 00:05:19.199
apart.'It

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.550
kept getting worse and worse, but

00:05:20.550 --> 00:05:20.560
I

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:21.749
kept praying

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:23.110
in the spirit

00:05:23.110 --> 00:05:23.120
and

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:24.870
laying hands on my mower: 'Mower, you're

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:26.550
