00:05:49.919 --> 00:05:51.590
You've got this. I thank You, Father,

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:54.150
that You supply for my

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:56.790
needs.'I

00:05:58.400 --> 00:05:59.909
