00:05:59.919 --> 00:06:01.510
'I'm not going to complain.'I thank You, Lord,

00:06:01.510 --> 00:06:01.520
that

00:06:01.520 --> 00:06:04.309
all my needs are met

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:05.990
