00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:08.070
this mower is even a concern to

00:06:08.070 --> 00:06:08.080
You.

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:09.830
I

00:06:09.830 --> 00:06:09.840
kept

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:12.309
mowing week after

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:14.550
week, and

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:16.550
