00:21:13.430 --> 00:21:13.440
changed—but

00:21:13.440 --> 00:21:16.149
if you keep on keeping on,

00:21:16.159 --> 00:21:18.070
if you keep speaking and you keep

00:21:18.080 --> 00:21:21.190
declaring and you keep looking at

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:22.870
your circumstances, it's

00:21:22.880 --> 00:21:26.149
going to change. It takes time sometimes to

00:21:26.159 --> 00:21:29.110
move a big ship and to turn a huge

00:21:29.120 --> 00:21:31.909
ocean liner. It takes a little bit to

00:21:31.919 --> 00:21:35.029
turn that ship. Sometimes it takes a

00:21:35.039 --> 00:21:36.630
little bit because you've been speaking

00:21:36.640 --> 00:21:38.950
so much trash out of your mouth for so

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:41.510
long. It may take a little bit, but

00:21:41.520 --> 00:21:44.470
don't give up. Don't give in to it.

00:21:44.480 --> 00:21:46.230
The devil might come by and whisper in

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:47.830
your ear, telling you your

00:21:47.840 --> 00:21:49.350
life's never going to change, you're

00:21:49.360 --> 00:21:51.430
going to be this way forever, and there's no

00:21:51.440 --> 00:21:53.990
God that hears your prayers. But I'm

00:21:54.000 --> 00:21:56.630
telling you this, God is faithful and

00:21:56.640 --> 00:21:58.710
He's going to set you free with the same

00:21:58.720 --> 00:22:01.029
power that He set me free with.

00:22:01.039 --> 00:22:04.149
He loves you. Don't get weary in

00:22:04.149 --> 00:22:04.159
well-doing.

00:22:04.159 --> 00:22:07.430
Keep your faith stirred

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:09.590
up. You've got to get in the word every

00:22:09.600 --> 00:22:11.750
day. You've got to get in prayer every

00:22:11.760 --> 00:22:14.390
day because you have to keep

00:22:14.390 --> 00:22:14.400
filling

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:17.190
your spirit up with that word.

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:19.909
Find the scripture. I've said

00:22:19.919 --> 00:22:22.230
it before and I'll say it again: you've got

00:22:22.240 --> 00:22:24.070
to find scriptures pertaining to what

00:22:24.080 --> 00:22:25.990
you're believing for. You've got to get

00:22:26.000 --> 00:22:28.230
that word down inside of your heart

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:30.549
because in those words, that's what

00:22:30.559 --> 00:22:32.470
brings freedom. You shall know the

00:22:32.480 --> 00:22:34.630
truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:22:34.640 --> 00:22:35.830
But I'm telling you, if you keep

00:22:35.840 --> 00:22:37.830
speaking trash out of your mouth, you're

00:22:37.840 --> 00:22:39.669
going to live it. I've

00:22:39.679 --> 00:22:41.669
lived it; I saw it happen

00:22:41.679 --> 00:22:43.909
when I was growing up. A lot of times my

00:22:43.919 --> 00:22:45.350
mom would speak things out of

00:22:45.360 --> 00:22:47.190
her mouth that she didn't believe in her

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:48.950
heart because whatever was at the

00:22:48.950 --> 00:22:48.960
abundance

00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:50.070
of the heart, the mouth speaks, what I

00:22:50.080 --> 00:22:51.669
tell you. And we

00:22:52.880 --> 00:22:54.070
kept going around the mountain. But I'm

00:22:54.080 --> 00:22:55.590
telling you, my mother started speaking

00:22:55.600 --> 00:22:57.510
better out of her mouth. She lives it

00:22:57.520 --> 00:22:59.430
now. She started speaking positive out

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:00.789
of her mouth. She started saying things

00:23:00.799 --> 00:23:03.510
over us: "It's going to get

00:23:03.510 --> 00:23:03.520
better."And

00:23:03.520 --> 00:23:05.430
I'm telling you, after the third kid,

00:23:05.440 --> 00:23:07.270
my little brother, he had it a lot

00:23:07.280 --> 00:23:09.190
better than what I had it. When I first

00:23:09.200 --> 00:23:11.190
started out, we had it real rough. But

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:12.470
when she started getting the word of

00:23:12.480 --> 00:23:13.990
faith and all that word down inside of

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:15.750
her, it started changing. My little

00:23:15.760 --> 00:23:16.789
brother has a totally different life

00:23:16.799 --> 00:23:18.710
than what I had. But I'm telling you

00:23:18.720 --> 00:23:22.070
this, you can change your circumstances

00:23:22.080 --> 00:23:25.110
by your words. You need to understand

00:23:25.120 --> 00:23:27.190
how powerful your words are. And I hope

00:23:27.200 --> 00:23:30.549
I haven't become boring, but I'm just

00:23:30.559 --> 00:23:32.230
trying to tell you what's changed my

00:23:32.240 --> 00:23:34.470
life. That's what I

00:23:34.480 --> 00:23:36.630
kept saying about the mower. God

00:23:36.640 --> 00:23:38.630
is a good God. He's going to take care

00:23:38.640 --> 00:23:40.470
of me. Even whenever it didn't look like

00:23:40.480 --> 00:23:41.990
it was going to and the

00:23:41.990 --> 00:23:42.000
summer is

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:43.990
almost over, but right when it's

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:45.830
almost time to start doing the leaves,

00:23:45.840 --> 00:23:48.149
God says, "Brennan, I got your back. I

00:23:48.159 --> 00:23:51.430
got you."Maybe He was talking to

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:54.310
that sister in the church for

00:23:54.320 --> 00:23:57.029
weeks ahead and she was

00:23:57.039 --> 00:23:59.270
resisting it. A lot of times, this is

00:23:59.280 --> 00:24:01.830
what I want to tell you: when God speaks

00:24:01.840 --> 00:24:04.710
to you to be obedient and to do

00:24:04.720 --> 00:24:07.750
something, do it immediately. Because if

00:24:07.760 --> 00:24:09.830
you don't, He'll bring that

00:24:09.840 --> 00:24:11.350
person who you're believing for

00:24:11.360 --> 00:24:13.029
and you're sowing those seeds. It may

00:24:13.039 --> 00:24:14.789
take you a long time. This might be

00:24:14.799 --> 00:24:17.190
something that I'm reaping. He might be

00:24:17.200 --> 00:24:18.310
telling you, 'You need to do this,

00:24:18.320 --> 00:24:20.149
this, and

00:24:20.149 --> 00:24:20.159
this.'He'll

00:24:20.159 --> 00:24:21.750
bring that same kind of

00:24:21.760 --> 00:24:23.830
person around you who was in

00:24:23.840 --> 00:24:26.230
rebellion. Basically, if he

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:28.230
told them a long time ago, 'I wanted

00:24:28.240 --> 00:24:30.149
to give that mower to them

00:24:30.159 --> 00:24:33.510
back in June or May when the season

00:24:33.520 --> 00:24:36.549
first started,'and they resisted

00:24:36.549 --> 00:24:36.559
it—'Oh,

00:24:36.559 --> 00:24:39.029
I don't feel like

00:24:39.029 --> 00:24:39.039
it.

00:24:39.039 --> 00:24:40.549
I don't want to do that. I just

00:24:40.559 --> 00:24:42.390
paid $7,000 for that'—and they wrestle

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:43.590
with it,

00:24:43.600 --> 00:24:46.470
the Lord keeps putting it on their heart: 'I

00:24:46.480 --> 00:24:48.950
want you to do this for Brandon.''I don't

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:52.710
feel like doing that right now, Lord.'Don't

00:24:52.710 --> 00:24:52.720
sow

00:24:52.720 --> 00:24:55.990
those kind of seeds. When God

00:24:56.000 --> 00:24:57.909
speaks to you to do something,

00:24:57.919 --> 00:25:00.470
be quick to obey because that's

00:25:00.480 --> 00:25:02.310
the kind of seed you'll reap back. When

00:25:02.320 --> 00:25:03.990
God speaks to somebody's heart to help

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:06.630
you out, be quick to obey.

00:25:08.159 --> 00:25:09.750
He'll start

00:25:09.760 --> 00:25:11.510
speaking to someone's heart to

00:25:11.510 --> 00:25:11.520
sow

00:25:11.520 --> 00:25:15.350
fast to

00:25:15.360 --> 00:25:17.269
you. You could be waiting on your

00:25:17.279 --> 00:25:18.950
miracle sometimes and ask, 'Where is it, Lord?'like

00:25:18.950 --> 00:25:18.960
in

00:25:18.960 --> 00:25:21.510
my situation. But

00:25:21.510 --> 00:25:21.520
there've

00:25:21.520 --> 00:25:23.350
been times he's told

00:25:23.360 --> 00:25:25.510
me, 'I want you to give a watch

00:25:25.510 --> 00:25:25.520
away.'I

00:25:25.520 --> 00:25:27.029
don't want to give that watch

00:25:27.039 --> 00:25:28.870
away because I love watches. Watches are a

00:25:28.880 --> 00:25:30.950
big deal to me. I've given seven watches

00:25:30.960 --> 00:25:33.190
away, and the Lord tells

00:25:33.200 --> 00:25:34.870
me it's like a ministry to me. I

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:37.350
love watches. So I give these

00:25:37.360 --> 00:25:38.789
watches away, and the Lord said,

00:25:38.799 --> 00:25:39.990
'See that person over there in

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:41.830
church? I want you to.'My first watch I

00:25:41.840 --> 00:25:43.909
ever gave away, I was 15 years old and I

00:25:43.919 --> 00:25:46.470
paid $400 for it; it was a

00:25:46.470 --> 00:25:46.480
Seiko.

00:25:46.480 --> 00:25:48.149
It was really dear to me because it was

00:25:48.159 --> 00:25:49.590
one of those kinetic ones

00:25:49.600 --> 00:25:50.789
that you could move your arm and

00:25:50.799 --> 00:25:53.110
it would charge itself.

00:25:53.120 --> 00:25:55.269
And the Lord spoke to me, 'I want you to

00:25:55.279 --> 00:25:57.830
give that watch to the youth

00:25:57.830 --> 00:25:57.840
pastor.'It

00:25:57.840 --> 00:26:01.110
was really nice back then; for me,

00:26:01.120 --> 00:26:02.549
that was a lot of money. It took me

00:26:02.559 --> 00:26:06.070
forever to save up for that watch.

00:26:06.080 --> 00:26:08.310
I kept resisting it and was like,

00:26:08.320 --> 00:26:10.390
'Please Lord, I don't want to give

00:26:10.400 --> 00:26:12.310
that watch away.'It took me

00:26:12.320 --> 00:26:14.149
months to save for that watch because I

00:26:14.159 --> 00:26:15.590
was sacking groceries,

00:26:15.600 --> 00:26:17.590
just

00:26:17.600 --> 00:26:19.190
putting groceries up, and I only

00:26:19.200 --> 00:26:21.510
made minimum wage. Back then,

00:26:21.520 --> 00:26:23.590
that was nothing. I kept

00:26:23.600 --> 00:26:25.350
resisting it and I didn't

00:26:25.360 --> 00:26:26.950
want to sow, but I had to do my tithes

00:26:26.950 --> 00:26:26.960
and

00:26:26.960 --> 00:26:28.230
offerings and everything. The Lord said, 'I

00:26:28.240 --> 00:26:31.029
want you to give that watch to

00:26:31.029 --> 00:26:31.039
him.'One

00:26:31.039 --> 00:26:33.190
day I was at church

00:26:33.200 --> 00:26:34.789
and he walked by me, and the Lord said,

00:26:34.799 --> 00:26:36.390
'Give that watch to him right now. I want

00:26:36.400 --> 00:26:38.310
you to be

00:26:38.320 --> 00:26:40.630
obedient to what I told you to do.'So I

00:26:40.640 --> 00:26:42.549
took my watch off and I said, 'Hey,

00:26:42.559 --> 00:26:44.710
pastor. The Lord spoke to me

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:46.789
to give this watch to you.

00:26:46.799 --> 00:26:48.630
This is a sacrificial gift,

00:26:48.630 --> 00:26:48.640
and

00:26:48.640 --> 00:26:51.110
it's painful for my

00:26:51.120 --> 00:26:53.590
flesh because it took me over three

00:26:53.600 --> 00:26:55.590
months to save up for this. 400

00:26:55.590 --> 00:26:55.600
bucks.'So

00:26:55.600 --> 00:26:58.149
I

00:26:58.159 --> 00:26:59.430
gave it to him and I prayed over him. I

00:26:59.440 --> 00:27:02.470
cried as I did it.

00:27:02.480 --> 00:27:04.789
But I'm trying to tell you, God

00:27:04.799 --> 00:27:06.789
is faithful and he always provides

00:27:06.799 --> 00:27:08.310
another watch. He always takes care of

00:27:08.320 --> 00:27:09.909
things. I started sowing those watches,

00:27:09.909 --> 00:27:09.919
and the

00:27:09.919 --> 00:27:11.110
Lord gives me better

00:27:11.110 --> 00:27:11.120
watches.

00:27:11.120 --> 00:27:13.350
So this is a thing for

00:27:13.360 --> 00:27:15.110
me.

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:17.669
I'm wanting you to understand

00:27:17.679 --> 00:27:19.669
that sometimes God will speak to your

00:27:19.679 --> 00:27:21.110
heart and tell you to do something

00:27:21.120 --> 00:27:22.789
that's not always comfortable to your

00:27:22.799 --> 00:27:24.630
flesh. It wasn't

00:27:24.640 --> 00:27:26.390
comfortable to the lady that gave me the

00:27:26.400 --> 00:27:29.110
$7,000 mower

00:27:29.120 --> 00:27:31.350
she just bought

00:27:31.360 --> 00:27:33.110
over a year ago. It was

00:27:33.120 --> 00:27:35.990
almost brand new.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:38.149
It's not comfortable sometimes.

00:27:38.159 --> 00:27:39.990
It makes you

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:42.070
want to go

00:27:42.070 --> 00:27:42.080
'ooh,'but

00:27:42.080 --> 00:27:44.230
there's reward

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:46.470
in it. There've been so many times

00:27:46.480 --> 00:27:48.710
that I sow and it's painful.

00:27:50.159 --> 00:27:51.590
But

00:27:51.600 --> 00:27:54.789
you have to move in faith for your

00:27:54.799 --> 00:27:56.470
circumstances. You've

00:27:56.470 --> 00:27:56.480
got

00:27:56.480 --> 00:27:59.510
to put your faith into motion

00:27:59.510 --> 00:27:59.520
and

00:27:59.520 --> 00:28:01.909
do things that

00:28:01.919 --> 00:28:04.149
are uncomfortable.

00:28:04.159 --> 00:28:06.389
God is a faithful God. And if you

00:28:06.389 --> 00:28:06.399
sow

00:28:06.399 --> 00:28:08.230
into good ground and you sow and you

00:28:08.240 --> 00:28:09.750
do these things, God will always come

00:28:09.760 --> 00:28:11.669
through for you. I'm just trying to tell

00:28:11.679 --> 00:28:13.669
you what I've lived, y'all.

00:28:15.440 --> 00:28:17.750
I do it all the time.

00:28:17.760 --> 00:28:20.470
And God is a faithful God. So if the

00:28:20.480 --> 00:28:22.389
Lord tells you to bless your church or

00:28:22.389 --> 00:28:22.399
the

00:28:22.399 --> 00:28:23.990
lady at

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:25.990
the grocery store and you don't want to

00:28:26.000 --> 00:28:28.630
help, she might be down

00:28:28.630 --> 00:28:28.640
to

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:30.950
her last $50.

00:28:33.679 --> 00:28:35.990
You could

00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:37.669
be the greatest influence and the

00:28:37.679 --> 00:28:40.230
greatest blessing to that person at that

00:28:40.240 --> 00:28:42.310
moment and

00:28:42.320 --> 00:28:44.389
just tell them, 'Jesus loves you and I

00:28:44.399 --> 00:28:45.510
just want to pray for you.'They

00:28:45.510 --> 00:28:45.520
may

00:28:45.520 --> 00:28:48.149
go, 'I need prayer.'Kind of

00:28:48.159 --> 00:28:49.430
like when I prayed for the man that had

00:28:49.440 --> 00:28:51.750
the bad lung problem. He was

00:28:51.760 --> 00:28:53.909
desperate and needed his

00:28:53.919 --> 00:28:55.350
miracle right then, or he

00:28:55.360 --> 00:28:57.430
was getting ready to die. What an

00:28:57.440 --> 00:28:59.110
opportunity to be a blessing!

00:28:59.120 --> 00:29:01.029
I

00:29:01.039 --> 00:29:02.549
see the comment section, and I'm just

00:29:02.559 --> 00:29:03.990
trying to go by what I see.

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:06.070
A

00:29:06.080 --> 00:29:07.669
lady's talking about how she's broke

00:29:07.669 --> 00:29:07.679
and

00:29:07.679 --> 00:29:09.269
can't pay for her food.

00:29:09.279 --> 00:29:10.630
I'm telling you how

00:29:10.640 --> 00:29:12.710
God's always provided for me. I

00:29:12.720 --> 00:29:14.630
wanted to tell you a testimony about

00:29:14.640 --> 00:29:16.789
what God did for me this evening just

00:29:16.799 --> 00:29:19.830
yesterday. God's so faithful and God

00:29:19.840 --> 00:29:21.190
will take care of you if you believe

00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:23.510
him. But you have to start speaking

00:29:23.510 --> 00:29:23.520
and

00:29:23.520 --> 00:29:25.110
believing

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:26.789
better. When you

00:29:26.799 --> 00:29:28.310
do,

00:29:28.320 --> 00:29:29.909
God's going to turn

00:29:29.919 --> 00:29:31.350
your mountain around. He's

00:29:31.360 --> 00:29:32.310
a

00:29:33.590 --> 00:29:33.600
mountain-dissolving

00:29:35.350 --> 00:29:35.360
God.

00:29:38.640 --> 00:29:41.990
We are

00:29:41.990 --> 00:29:42.000
in

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:45.510
the greatest days for the

00:29:45.520 --> 00:29:47.190
body of Christ to be a light

00:29:47.190 --> 00:29:47.200
and

00:29:47.200 --> 00:29:50.310
to be the salt. It's a choice. But

00:29:50.320 --> 00:29:54.789
Jesus needs us to

00:29:54.799 --> 00:29:56.870
be obedient. If we're not,

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:58.070
we're not doing what he's called us to

00:29:58.080 --> 00:29:59.750
do.

00:30:03.919 --> 00:30:05.909
He's ready to come back, but

00:30:05.919 --> 00:30:07.269
he's wanting those souls coming in.

00:30:07.279 --> 00:30:09.110
If you have something on

00:30:09.120 --> 00:30:10.789
your heart and you need direction,

00:30:10.799 --> 00:30:13.510
or for

00:30:13.520 --> 00:30:15.110
preaching like

00:30:15.120 --> 00:30:16.389
these little sermons I'm

00:30:16.389 --> 00:30:16.399
doing,

00:30:16.399 --> 00:30:17.990
tell me, 'Hey, I'm

00:30:18.000 --> 00:30:19.430
believing for

00:30:19.440 --> 00:30:21.190
this.'I'm

00:30:21.200 --> 00:30:22.549
trying to

00:30:22.559 --> 00:30:24.549
give you encouragement by

00:30:24.549 --> 00:30:24.559
telling you

00:30:24.559 --> 00:30:26.389
how my wife and I have lived

00:30:26.399 --> 00:30:27.990
this. We're not

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:30.710
perfect. One time we

00:30:30.720 --> 00:30:34.230
had our maternity and the

00:30:34.240 --> 00:30:36.549
doctor's bills were thousands of

00:30:36.559 --> 00:30:39.830
dollars. We were

00:30:39.840 --> 00:30:41.029
broke.

00:30:41.039 --> 00:30:42.630
I was working at the church and we

00:30:42.640 --> 00:30:46.230
were real desperate. The

00:30:46.240 --> 00:30:48.870
hospital sent the bill to

00:30:48.870 --> 00:30:48.880
a

00:30:48.880 --> 00:30:51.110
collection agency,

00:30:51.120 --> 00:30:52.549
and they were going

00:30:52.559 --> 00:30:54.789
to garnish our wages.

00:30:54.799 --> 00:30:57.190
It's the way it is here in Oklahoma.

00:30:57.200 --> 00:31:00.070
If you don't pay

00:31:00.080 --> 00:31:01.590
your bills,

00:31:01.600 --> 00:31:03.110
they're able to come after

00:31:03.120 --> 00:31:04.710
you.

00:31:04.720 --> 00:31:06.950
Rightfully so, I owed the money, but

00:31:06.960 --> 00:31:08.950
I just didn't have it.

00:31:13.039 --> 00:31:14.230
We were living on food stamps.

00:31:14.230 --> 00:31:14.240
They were

00:31:14.240 --> 00:31:15.430
saying, 'We're going to garnish your

00:31:15.430 --> 00:31:15.440
checks.'We

