00:32:14.480 --> 00:32:16.870
God and

00:32:16.880 --> 00:32:20.389
rejoice. Keep your eyes on Jesus. Don't

00:32:20.399 --> 00:32:22.950
put your eyes on man. My wife, Diana,

00:32:22.960 --> 00:32:24.149
